<paragraph id="E51436D9FF90FFCDC9ADFE9457C0FEA4" blockId="35.[138,1185,313,370]" pageId="35" pageNumber="813">
Hyères— 
<emphasis id="D7DFEACBFF90FFCDC9D1FE94523BFE84" box="[246,379,314,338]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="813">Seamount 2</emphasis>
